==English==
===Noun===
'''whatchamacallit''' ([[whatchamacallits]])

# a metasyntactic term used for any object whose actual name you don't know or can't remember. There are many spellings and many synonyms.

====Synonyms====
*[[dohickey]], [[doohickey]]
*[[doober]]
*[[doodad]]
*[[doover]] (''Australia'')
*[[thingamabob]], [[thingumabob]], [[thingummybob]]
*[[thingamajig]]
*[[thingo]] (''Australia'')
*[[thingummy]]
*[[whatnot]]
*[[whatsit]]

